            <p>—The letter from EC arrived,<ptr target="bol.00003_n3"/> with contents—all safe. I return
                heartfelt thanks—am only middling well in health, but get about the house,
                &amp; write a little<ptr target="bol.00003_n1"/>—</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
